gobblin.data.management.convertion.hive

Class HiveSource

  • java.lang.Object
    • gobblin.data.management.convertion.hive.HiveSource
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Source

    public class HiveSource
extends Object
implements Source

    A Source that creates generic workunits for a hive table or a hive partition.

    • It uses the HiveDatasetFinder to find all hive tables and partitions
    • The update time of a hive Table or a hive Partition if found using HiveUnitUpdateProvider
    • The update time from the previous run is used as previous hive watermark.HiveSourceWatermarker is used to get previous hive watermarks
    WorkUnits are created if the previous high watermark of a Partition or a Table are lower than the latest update time.

    The WorkUnits contain a serialized json of the HiveTable or HivePartition at "hive.unit.serialized" This is later deserialized by the extractor.
